# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Semantic Search / Embeddings
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Option A: Local llama.cpp server (Qwen3-Embedding-0.6B, no API key needed)
#   1. cd packages/adapters/embedding-local && pnpm setup && pnpm start
#   2. Set these vars:
# EMBEDDING_PROVIDER=local
# EMBEDDING_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8085
# EMBEDDING_MODEL=Qwen3-Embedding-0.6B
# EMBEDDING_DIMENSIONS=1024

# Option B: OpenAI text-embedding-3-small (requires API key)
# EMBEDDING_PROVIDER=openai
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# EMBEDDING_MODEL=text-embedding-3-small
# EMBEDDING_DIMENSIONS=1536
